io.reinert.requestor

Interface HasHttpSendMethods

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    RequestSender

    public interface HasHttpSendMethods
    Defines HTTP request invocation methods. NOTE: This class is removed from classpath when assembling the jar. Implementers should provide an own implementation exposing a preferred Promises API. Implementers must follow the pattern of this class in order to be officially integrated.
    Author:
    Danilo Reinert
    See Also:
    RequestSender
